ivardefs.name: altitude
ivardefs.desc: Altitude. The value domain and the interpretation are the same as for the text of the altitude element in KML (see notes below).

ivardefs.name: latitude
ivardefs.desc: Latitude. The value domain and the interpretation are the same as for the text of the latitude element in KML (see notes below).

ivardefs.name: longitude
ivardefs.desc: Longitude. The value domain and the interpretation are the same as for the text of the longitude element in KML (see notes below).

properties.desc: The absolute geographic location of the Location, expressed using the WGS84 datum (This is the same co-ordinate system used in KML).
